PN,39901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FA registered sex offender has been
OL,7,Fjailed after he was identified by Live
OL,8,FFacial Recognition technology
OL,9,Fbreaching restrictions placed on him.
OL,11,FJohn Thompson, 43, from Manchester,
OL,12,Fwas spotted by police cameras in
OL,13,FPiccadilly Gardens on 28 January after
OL,14,Fbeing placed on a watchlist monitored
OL,15,Fby officers.
OL,17,FThe alert was triggered by one of
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Police's Live
OL,19,FFacial Recognition (LFR) vans, which
OL,20,Fhave been used across the region since
OL,21,FOctober 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FOfficers approached Thompson following
OL,7,Fthe match and he admitted he had an
OL,8,Fadditional mobile phone in his
OL,9,Fpossession ` a direct breach of the
OL,10,FSexual Harm Prevention Order (SHPO)
OL,11,Fimposed on him.
OL,13,FThompson, whose date of birth is 10
OL,14,FJune 1982, later admitted to a total
OL,15,Fof 35 breaches of his SHPO and a
OL,16,Fbreach of his sex offender
OL,17,Fnotification requirements.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 16 months in
OL,7,Fprison when he appeared at Manchester
OL,8,FCrown Court on Tuesday 3 March. He was
OL,9,Falso ordered to pay #187 in costs.
OL,11,FPolice said that without the use of
OL,12,FLive Facial Recognition, the extent of
OL,13,FThompson's non-compliance could have
OL,14,Fgone unnoticed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said around
OL,7,F20% of arrests made using the
OL,8,Ftechnology since it was introduced
OL,9,Fhave involved registered sex
OL,10,Foffenders, and about three-quarters of
OL,11,Fsuspects identified through the system
OL,12,Fhave gone on to be charged with
OL,13,Foffences.
OL,15,FInspector Jon Middleton said the case
OL,16,Fshowed the value of the technology in
OL,17,Fhelping officers intervene quickly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,F"This is a great result and shows
OL,7,Fexactly why we are using Live Facial
OL,8,FRecognition not only across Greater
OL,9,FManchester but further afield in the
OL,10,Fnorth west," he said.
OL,12,F"LFR bolsters our policing teams to
OL,13,Fprotect the public, locate individuals
OL,14,Fwho are wanted by the courts, and
OL,15,Fensure offenders continue to comply
OL,16,Fwith the conditions placed upon them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,F"When a match is confirmed, officers
OL,7,Fcan intervene before a suspect has the
OL,8,Fopportunity to commit further
OL,9,Foffences, significantly reducing the
OL,10,Frisk to innocent members of the
OL,11,Fpublic."
OL,13,FHe added that the system enhances the
OL,14,Fwork of neighbourhood policing teams
OL,15,Fand allows officers to focus resources
OL,16,Fwhere they are most needed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Jen
OL,7,FTattersall, from GMP's Public
OL,8,FProtection Division, said the
OL,9,Ftechnology was strengthening how
OL,10,Fpolice manage registered sex offenders.
OL,12,F"It enables us to identify, in real
OL,13,Ftime, individuals who are breaching
OL,14,Flicence conditions, entering
OL,15,Fprohibited areas, or ignoring Sexual
OL,16,FHarm Prevention Order restrictions,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,F"In this case, LFR meant officers
OL,7,Fcould intervene swiftly, uncovering an
OL,8,Fadditional mobile phone in the
OL,9,Foffender's possession which was an
OL,10,Fexplicit breach of his SHPO.
OL,12,F"This is exactly why we use LFR; it
OL,13,Fgives us a more proactive,
OL,14,Fintelligence-led, and robust approach
OL,15,Fto managing sexual offenders."
OL,17,FLive Facial Recognition vans supplied
OL,18,Fby the Home Office are being used by
OL,19,Fpolice forces across the north west.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
