OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772802691
OL,3,CSex offender jailed after facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology identifies him
OL,6,FThey will next be deployed in Rochdale
OL,7,Fon Thursday 12 March and in Manchester
OL,8,Fcity centre the following day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
